{"tid":1259052,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」民建聯開始怕了 加強蛇齋餅糭攻勢！","createTime":"2019-06-26T12:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T04:47:28.000Z","uid":10426,"like":441,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5ff2d530df02a6b34c09a87b2e0a4ed71df9ff","tid":1259052,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說小弟係石籬呢啲出哂名多廢老的社區成長，不過幸好當區區議員仲係民主黨揸旗。<br />\n<br />\n不過自從幾年前民建聯派啲所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">靚女社區主任</span></span>之後，民主黨的聲勢每況愈下，連佢地都要搞下蛇齋餅糭留住班廢佬嘅選票，不過幾平都比唔過民建聯阿爺條水喉.....<br />\n<br />\n直到呢排反送中事件，上連登見到有巴打話民建聯加強蛇齋餅糭的攻勢，今日就收到電話話民建聯個社區主任叫佢拎米，仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個人派五公斤，又派水樽又盛！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明民建聯已經開始怕因爲送中失去區議會議席，各位巴打要留意屋企人有冇中伏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awcMuNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawcMuNo.png&h=b39d660b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有呢張證十成十係入左民建聯會！各位巴打記住，米照攞，票唔投！要佢地票債票償！</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15bbc4103a39018798273dfeed83fac10a4d6f93","tid":1259052,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5310b0993c881661aace3b7405f3f039576f18f8","tid":1259052,"uid":34515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［置頂］今晚八點 中環愛丁堡廣場見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"9014c803e320c24e2a282a00c61acc5d42642cac","tid":1259052,"uid":10426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc