":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說小弟係石籬呢啲出哂名多廢老的社區成長，不過幸好當區區議員仲係民主黨揸旗。<br />\n<br />\n不過自從幾年前民建聯派啲所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">靚女社區主任</span></span>之後，民主黨的聲勢每況愈下，連佢地都要搞下蛇齋餅糭留住班廢佬嘅選票，不過幾平都比唔過民建聯阿爺條水喉.....<br />\n<br />\n直到呢排反送中事件，上連登見到有巴打話民建聯加強蛇齋餅糭的攻勢，今日就收到電話話民建聯個社區主任叫佢拎米，仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個人派五公斤，又派水樽又盛！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明民建聯已經開始怕因爲送中失去區議會議席，各位巴打要留意屋企人有冇中伏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awcMuNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawcMuNo.png&h=b39d660b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有呢張證十成十係入左民建聯會！各位巴打記住，米照攞，票唔投！要佢地票債票償！</span></span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔知呢度啲連登仔知唔知<br />\n以前毓民個時08年立法會選舉口號係「食窮民建聯，票投社民連」<br />\n呢度啲人識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a3308588d1101a2293946e368a0fbe8aaf3065","tid":1259052,"uid":7427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0193de2a2930b06befd4d12b801679210cbbcd71","tid":1259052,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a1a6e0850eee34690191a5782b4cfdd70abd2f5","tid":1259052,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2194114270af1af2b17e722e44832db5e7da05","tid":1259052,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed51e1cd59616a883829d4b953195f1eea60ca98","tid":1259052,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"石蔭以前係尹兆堅<br />\n好似差幾十票輸比肥仔<br />\n今年佢會唔會再返黎選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c